ActNational Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians Act
PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE PATRICIA DUNCAN, a member of the Senate, to be a member of the National Security and Intelligence Committee of Parliamentarians, to hold office during pleasure until the dissolution of Parliament following her appointment.
